rComments: Chose very interesting works for us to read, but he's such a tough grader!  Feedback could be pretty harsh too.
One of the best profs I've ever had. If you're serious about English, take his class.

Childs is my favourite professor of all time. He is smart and sharply witty and and an amazing teacher. I can't wait to take his fourth year course. You have to be respectful and want to be there - otherwise he wants nothing to do with you. But if you apply yourself and have a sense of humour, you should do just fine.
